{"data":[{"date":"08:34 28/06","title":"Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec trong ng\u00e0y Brazil nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng h\u1ea1 Serbia 2-0?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/thay-gi-trong-ngay-brazil-nhe-nhang-ha-serbia-20.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Brazil vs Serbia kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ee7ng \u0111\u1ec9nh nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ea7y hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Samba. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i chi ti\u1ebft \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd kh\u00e1c trong m\u00e0n so t\u00e0i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Otkrytiye Arena.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Serbia 0-2 Brazil\r\n<div style=\"text - align:center; width: 100 %; padding: 20px 0; \"><video class=\"hlsvideoobj\" data-src=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/DRM/HLS/201806/274130/master.m3u8\" controls=\"\"></video></div>\r\n</em></div>\r\n<h2>Brazil nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBrazil b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Serbia b\u1eb1ng t\u00e2m th\u1ebf kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ea5t thi\u1ebft ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1. M\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 Selecao ghi t\u00ean m\u00ecnh v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta kh\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 n\u00f4n n\u00f3ng t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Brazil gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Serbia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Tite \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec1 ra m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt \u01b0u ti\u00ean s\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u1ee7a Brazil \u0111\u1eb7t l\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. Trong th\u1ebf bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i d\u00e2ng cao \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh, Serbia \u0111\u00e3 r\u01a1i v\u00e0o b\u1eaby m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Samba gi\u0103ng ra. Ph\u00fat 36, t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n d\u00e0i si\u00eau h\u1ea1ng c\u1ee7a Philippe Coutinho, \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a anh t\u1ea1i Barcelona l\u00e0 Paulinho c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Stojkovic v\u00e0 nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec trong ng\u00e0y Brazil nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng h\u1ea1 Serbia 2-0 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec trong ng\u00e0y Brazil nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng h\u1ea1 Serbia 2-0 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/Brazil-nhe-nhang-vuot-qua-Serbia.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Brazil kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Serbia 2-0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nK\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3, Brazil c\u00e0ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. Serbia kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed khoa h\u1ecdc c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, Brazil c\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u00eam 1 b\u00e0n n\u1eefa do c\u00f4ng Thiago Silva xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c c\u1ee7a Neymar.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong ng\u00e0y \u0110\u1ee9c b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c trong vi\u1ec7c c\u00f3 d\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u00e0 s\u1edbm b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i, Brazil l\u1ea1i nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng E. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 VCK World Cup th\u1ee9 13 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong 12 l\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Brazil 3 l\u1ea7n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch (1970, 1994 v\u00e0 2002), 1 l\u1ea7n v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft (1998), 1 l\u1ea7n \u0111o\u1ea1t gi\u1ea3i 3 (1978) v\u00e0 2 l\u1ea7n c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch th\u1ee9 4 (1974 v\u00e0 2014). V\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00f4i sao c\u00f9ng phong c\u00e1ch h\u1ee3p th\u1eddi, Selecao h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd c\u00f2n \u1edf l\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga cho t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u00f4ng Marcelo, kh\u00f4ng sao</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c Marcelo d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 r\u1eddi s\u00e2n ngay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 10 \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u C\u0110V Brazil lo l\u1eafng. N\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y s\u1ea3y ch\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Serbia, \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Brazil vs Serbia s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eafc t\u1edbi t\u00ean c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f9ng Real Madrid v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League 3 m\u00f9a li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec trong ng\u00e0y Brazil nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng h\u1ea1 Serbia 2-0 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec trong ng\u00e0y Brazil nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng h\u1ea1 Serbia 2-0 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/Thay-gi-trong-ngay-Brazil-nhe-nhang-ha-Serbia-2-0-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">S\u1ef1 v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Marcelo kh\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn Selecao qu\u00e1 lo ng\u1ea1i</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, Marcelo v\u1eabn c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t, nh\u01b0ng theo chi\u1ec1u h\u01b0\u1edbng l\u1ea1c quan h\u01a1n cho Brazil. S\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf mang t\u00ean Filipe Luis h\u1eb3n v\u1eabn khi\u1ebfn HLV Tite h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng. C\u00f3 Marcelo tr\u00ean s\u00e2n, Brazil s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cung c\u1ea5p th\u00eam nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng song \u0111\u00f4i l\u00fac phong c\u00e1ch d\u00e2ng cao c\u1ee7a anh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t y\u1ebfu \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 khai th\u00e1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi Brazil, b\u00ean c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ngh\u1ec7 s\u0129 nh\u01b0 Neymar v\u00e0 Coutinho hi\u1ec7n di\u1ec7n. Nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Filipe \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Serbia, anh r\u1ea5t ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p trong vai tr\u00f2 b\u1ecdc l\u00f3t cho hai ng\u00f4i sao tr\u00ean. V\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf Atletico Madrid \u1edf ph\u00eda sau, Neymar v\u00e0 Coutinho c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng s\u1ee3 kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng l\u1edbn m\u00e0 Marcelo hay \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i ph\u00eda sau.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-brazil-vs-serbia-461-189793.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/clip-ban-thang-brazil-vs-serbia.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-brazil-vs-serbia-461-189793.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Serbia 0-2 Brazil (B\u1ea3ng E World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\n<span>Kh\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n, Selecao ch\u1eb3ng g\u1eb7p qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ea1nh tranh tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Serbia. H\u1ecd \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ebfn cu\u1ed1i v\u00e0 x\u1ee9ng...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u01b0a r\u00f5 m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Marcelo, nh\u01b0ng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t v\u1ebft \u0111au th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u00edch c\u1ee7a Filipe, Brazil kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i qu\u00e1 \u00e2u lo v\u1ec1 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 Serbia c\u00f2n h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 \u0111\u1eb7t Serbia v\u00e0o t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t. Th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u1edf ph\u00fat 36 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 bi\u1ec7t danh &ldquo;\u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng&rdquo; c\u00e0ng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n h\u01a1n n\u1eefa. Khi \u0111\u00f3, c\u00e1c C\u0110V ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i s\u1ef1 qu\u1eadt kh\u1edfi t\u1eeb Serbia \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u k\u1ef3 di\u1ec7u l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien dao Mitrovic tiec nuoi\" title=\"tien dao Mitrovic tiec nuoi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/tien-dao-Mitrovic-tiec-nuoi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Serbia d\u1eebng ch\u00e2n ngay sau v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng x\u1ea3y ra. \u0110\u1ebfn 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, Serbia c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 hu\u1ed1ng chi l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd t\u1edbi sau c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a ch\u1ee7 c\u00f4ng Alek Mitrovic. Trong t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00f3, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t Fagner 1m68, \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eadt l\u00ean r\u1ea5t cao nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng tr\u00fang v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Alisson.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u00f3 n\u00f3i l\u00ean \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a Serbia ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil. Gi\u1ea3 s\u1eed Selecao mu\u1ed1n t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n thay v\u00ec \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng hay ch\u00ed \u00edt l\u00e0 ch\u1eaft chiu c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i h\u01a1n, s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n thua c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng thu\u1ed9c Nam T\u01b0 c\u0169 s\u1ebd c\u00f2n gia t\u0103ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-brazil-vs-serbia-463-189782.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/clip-ban-thang-brazil-vs-serbia.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-brazil-vs-serbia-463-189782.html\">Serbia 0-2 Brazil (KT): D\u1ea1o ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i Moscow, Selecao k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1ed1 1</span><br>\r\n<span>Kh\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n, Selecao ch\u1eb3ng g\u1eb7p qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ea1nh tranh tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Serbia. H\u1ecd \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ebfn cu\u1ed1i v\u00e0 x\u1ee9ng...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSerbia v\u1eabn c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u. Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ec3 ra Milinkovic-Savic, Nemanja Matic hay Alek Kolarov. Nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 g\u00e1nh v\u00e1c n\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 Serbia t\u1ea7m th\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 tr\u1ecdng tr\u00e1ch &ldquo;Ng\u1ef1a \u00f4&rdquo; \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c giao tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi v\u00e0o gi\u1ea3i l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 s\u1ee9c.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>C\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i v\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a Brazil</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1ed7i khi Brazil thi \u0111\u1ea5u, m\u1ecdi \u00e1nh m\u1eaft \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ed3n v\u00e0o Neymar. Ti\u1ebfc l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 x\u1ee9 Samba l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u1ea1i m\u1edbi b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u00e0n ch\u00e2n kh\u00e1 n\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y 1 th\u00e1ng. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi n\u1ed7i lo t\u00e1i ph\u00e1t ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c l\u00fac ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Neymar \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1ed1i \u01b0u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Serbia vs Brazil Coutinho di bong\" title=\"Serbia vs Brazil Coutinho di bong\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/Serbia-vs-Brazil-Coutinho-di-bong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Coutinho l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Brazil vs Serbia</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, m\u1ed7i m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00f4i qua, Neymar l\u1ea1i ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n. \u1ede tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n, &ldquo;Ti\u1ec3u Pele&rdquo; im ti\u1ebfng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e1 r\u1eafn \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n anh. Nh\u01b0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Costa Rica, Neymar \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1ea3i t\u1ecfa s\u1ee9c \u00e9p v\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 cho Brazil. V\u00e0 m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Serbia, Neymar ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n v\u1edbi qu\u1ea3 t\u1ea1t ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c \u0111\u1ec3 Thiago Silva ghi b\u00e0n. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Brazil vs Serbia s\u1ebd l\u00e0 thi\u1ebfu s\u00f3t n\u1ebfu b\u1ecf qua Coutinho. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n t\u1eeb ni\u00ean thi\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a Neymar g\u00f3p d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y trong c\u1ea3 3 tr\u1eadn v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a Selecao. Sau 1 b\u00e0n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y S\u0129, 1 b\u00e0n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Costa Rica, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Barcelona l\u1ea1i tung \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n tuy\u1ec7t h\u1ea3o gi\u00fap Paulinho khai th\u00f4ng b\u1ebf t\u1eafc tr\u01b0\u1edbc Serbia.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-brazil-noi-gi-sau-chien-thang-truoc-serbia-421-189815.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/ngoi-sao-thu-5-va-nhung-giac-mo-con-dang-do.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-brazil-noi-gi-sau-chien-thang-truoc-serbia-421-189815.html\">HLV Brazil n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Serbia?</span><br>\r\nHLV Tite ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Brazil vs Serbia, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 57 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Selecao c\u00e0ng ch\u01a1i c\u00e0ng hay \u1edf World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u01a1n t\u1edbi gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 6 trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed, Brazil s\u1ebd d\u1ef1a nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o Neymar v\u00e0 Coutinho. \u0110\u1ebfn gi\u1edd, h\u1ecd v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thong so tran dau Serbia 0-2 Brazil\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Serbia 0-2 Brazil\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/Thong-so-Brazil.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Serbia 0-2 Brazil</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Brazil 2-0 Serbia tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-thong-ke-dang-nho-sau-tran-dau-brazil-20-serbia-421-189806.html\">Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Brazil 2-0 Serbia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/brazil-nhan-tin-du-sau-khi-danh-bai-serbia-469-189804.html\">Brazil nh\u1eadn tin d\u1eef sau khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Serbia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hlv-serbia-khang-dinh-choi-tren-chan-brazil-465-189798.html\">HLV Mladen Krstajic: Serbia ch\u01a1i tr\u00ean ch\u00e2n Brazil trong hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-brazil-vs-serbia-461-189793.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Serbia 0-2 Brazil (B\u1ea3ng E World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-brazil-vs-serbia-421-189790.html\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Serbia vs Brazil tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng E World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-brazil-vs-serbia-463-189782.html\">Serbia 0-2 Brazil (KT): D\u1ea1o ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i Moscow, Selecao k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1ed1 1</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"665","check