tyle=\"text-align: center; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">VTV6</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"border:1px solid #dddddd;\">\r\n            <div style=\"text-align: center;\">29/06 01:00</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">B\u1ec9 - Anh</td>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">VTV6</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">29/06 01:00</td>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">Tunisia - Panama</td>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">VTV3</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"664","checkdouble":"189809"},{"date":"08:42 28/06","title":"Kaka m\u00e1ch n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ec3 \u0110T Brazil gi\u00fap Neymar t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i World Cup","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/kaka-mach-nuoc-de-dt-brazil-bien-neymar-toa-sang-tai-world-cup.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Neymar ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Kaka tin r\u1eb1ng BHL \u0110T Brazil n\u00ean h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi c\u00e1ch ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Ronaldo.</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Neymar b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o VCK World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 phong \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea1t tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u1ea5t sau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng\u00a0r\u1ea1n x\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u00e0n ch\u00e2n g\u1eb7p \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa PSG v\u00e0 Marseille h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 3 v\u1eeba qua.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kaka m\u00e1ch n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ec3 \u0110T Brazil gi\u00fap Neymar t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i World Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Kaka m\u00e1ch n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ec3 \u0110T Brazil gi\u00fap Neymar t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i World Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/kaka-mach-nuoc-de-dt-brazil-bien-neymar-toa-sang-tai-world-cup.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Kaka tin r\u1eb1ng Neymar s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p \u00e1p l\u1ef1c</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i v\u00ec sao ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u2018nh\u1eefng v\u0169 c\u00f4ng Samba\u2019 ch\u01b0a t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng nh\u01b0 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng. T\u00ednh t\u1edbi th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Neymar m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 duy nh\u1ea5t 1 b\u00e0n t\u1ea1i World Cup v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Costa Rica.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y, c\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Kaka cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia c\u1ea7n thay \u0111\u1ed5i c\u00e1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Neymar, nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111ang l\u00e0m v\u1edbi Cristiano Ronaldo. Qu\u1ea3 B\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng 2007 cho bi\u1ebft: \"\u00c1p l\u1ef1c l\u00ean m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao nh\u01b0 Neymar kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd l\u00e0 b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean g\u1eb7p Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng. T\u00f4i t\u1eebng tr\u1ea3i qua c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c \u1ea5y, khi ra qu\u00e2n \u1edf World Cup, v\u00e0 bi\u1ebft c\u1ea3m x\u00fac l\u00fac \u0111\u00f3 \u00e2u lo nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o. Th\u1eadt m\u1eebng l\u00e0 Neymar r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1eddi nay kh\u00e1c xa th\u1eddi t\u00f4i ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng. B\u00e2y gi\u1edd, truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng v\u00e0 m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i hi\u1ec7n di\u1ec7n m\u1ecdi l\u00fac m\u1ecdi n\u01a1i trong cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng. Ai c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm th\u00f4ng tin tr\u00ean \u0111\u00f3. Brazil c\u1ea7n h\u1ecdc c\u00e1ch B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m v\u1edbi Cristiano Ronaldo. H\u00e3y \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u00f4i sao s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t th\u1ea3 l\u1ecfng v\u00e0 t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng g\u00ec h\u1ecd th\u00edch\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, Kaka c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1eddi khuy\u00ean r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Brazil c\u1ea7n h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 Neymar \u0111\u1ec3 anh s\u1edbm l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i phong \u0111\u1ed9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"Neymar c\u1ea7n th\u00eam th\u1eddi gian. Ch\u00fang ta v\u1eabn nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y qua t\u1eebng tr\u1eadn. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 cho \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Neymar v\u00e0 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i ng\u00e0y c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111i\u1ec3m r\u01a1i phong \u0111\u1ed9. N\u1ebfu c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i 100% th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng, Brazil ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 s\u00e1u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi\", Kaka n\u00f3i th\u00eam.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Serbia v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-0 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i, Brazil s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng F l\u00e0 Mexico t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra l\u00fac 21h00 ng\u00e0y 2/7 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-thong-ke-dang-nho-sau-tran-dau-brazil-20-serbia-421-189806.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/nhung-thong-ke-dang-nho-sau-tran-dau-brazil-20-serbia.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-thong-ke-dang-nho-sau-tran-dau-brazil-20-serbia-421-189806.html\">Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Brazil 2-0 Serbia</span><br>\r\nD\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Brazil 2-0 Serbia l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 3 b\u1ea3ng E VCK World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/brazil-nhan-tin-du-sau-khi-danh-bai-serbia-469-189804.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/brazil-nhan-tin-du-sau-khi-danh-bai-serbia.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/brazil-nhan-tin-du-sau-khi-danh-bai-serbia-469-189804.html\">Brazil nh\u1eadn tin d\u1eef sau khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Serbia</span><br>\r\nH\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Marcelo \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb r\u00fat ra kh\u1ecfi s\u00e2n s\u1edbm trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Brazil v\u00e0 Serbia \u0111\u00eam qua v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/danh-bai-mexico-augustinsson-thach-thuc-dt-brazil-465-189787.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/danh-bai-mexico-augustinsson-thach-thuc-dt-brazil.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/danh-bai-mexico-augustinsson-thach-thuc-dt-brazil-465-189787.html\">\u0110\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Mexico, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng \u0110T Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n l\u1edbn ti\u1ebfng th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c Brazil</span><br>\r\nGhi b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ec3 g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Mexico, Ludwig Augustinsson th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c \u0110T Brazil, \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"663","checkdouble":"189811"},{"date":"08:27 28/06","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n vs Ba Lan (21h00 ng\u00e0y 26/06): Ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/nhan-dinh-nhat-ban-vs-ba-lan-21h00-ngay-2606-niem-hy-vong-cuoi-cung.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n vs Ba Lan trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c1 ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, song th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Nishino Akira v\u1eabn s\u1ebd chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t \u201c\u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng tr\u1eafng\u201d \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c1</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf World Cup 2018, trong s\u1ed1 5 \u0111\u1ed9i tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga th\u00ec 4 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i. Theo \u0111\u00f3 Saudi Arabia, Iran, Australia v\u00e0 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n vs Ba Lan (21h00, 2606) Hy v\u1ecdng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n vs Ba Lan (21h00, 2606) Hy v\u1ecdng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/Nhan-dinh-Nhat-Ban-vs-Ba-Lan-(21h00,-2606)-Hy-vong-cuoi-cung-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00e2u \u00c1</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nN\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Saudi Arabia, Iran v\u00e0 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng th\u00ec Australia ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau 3 tr\u1eadn. T\u1ed1i nay, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n v\u00e0 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c1 l\u00e0 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Ba Lan.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf hoa Anh \u0111\u00e0o \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t \u1edf World Cup 2018, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng H, song th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Nishino Akira li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 nu\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/tuong-thuat-colombia-vs-nhat-ban-463-188923.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Colombia 2-1</span>. Ph\u1ea3i th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c1 c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf ch\u01a1i h\u01a1n ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t s\u1edbm, song h\u1ecd c\u0169ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh khi Colombia d\u1ed3n to\u00e0n l\u1ef1c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ee9c \u00e9p r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 2 v\u1edbi Senegal, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf hoa Anh \u0111\u00e0o ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i ki\u00ean c\u01b0\u1eddng, d\u00f9 hai l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u Phi v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd v\u1eabn xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 2-2.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nShinji Kagawa v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t \u1edf World Cup 2018, h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00f4i sao, nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh b\u1eb1ng tinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ec1n b\u1ec9 v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e0n k\u1ebft.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau 2 tr\u1eadn, Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111ang c\u00f9ng c\u00f3 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u01b0 Senegal \u1edf b\u1ea3ng H, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng \u0111ang r\u1ed9ng m\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eb7t th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Nishino Akira.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n vs Ba Lan trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u1edf b\u1ea3ng H, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng gi\u1edd Colombia \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Senegal. \u1ede b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0 Senegal \u0111ang c\u00f3 c\u00f9ng 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m, Colombia x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 3 v\u1edbi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f2n Ba Lan x\u1ebfp b\u00e9t b\u1ea3ng khi ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0o.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Preview Nhat Ban vs Ba Lan\" title=\"Preview Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n vs Ba Lan\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/Nhat-Ban-vs-Ba-Lan.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n vs Ba Lan trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c1 ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111i ti\u1ebfp</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nV\u1edbi c\u1ee5c di\u1ec7n b\u1ea3ng H hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n h\u00f2a Ba Lan l\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u00f3 v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp. Nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 gi\u00e0nh \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc &ldquo;\u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng tr\u1eafng&rdquo; kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 kh\u00f3 nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1eadm ch\u00ed, ngay c\u1ea3 khi \u0111\u1ec3 thua Ba Lan \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u1eabn s\u1ebd \u0111i ti\u1ebfp n\u1ebfu Senegal \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Colombia \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng gi\u1edd.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Akira Nishino kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ec3 v\u1eadn m\u1ec7nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c, khi c\u00f3 trong tay quy\u1ec1n t\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft h\u1ecd s\u1ebd chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1edf toang c\u00e1nh c\u1eeda v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n5 l\u1ea7n tham d\u1ef1 World Cup g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n c\u00f3 2 l\u1ea7n v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea ch\u1ec9 ra r\u1eb1ng c\u1ee9 sau 1 l\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng th\u00ec h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 1 l\u1ea7n \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 4 n\u0103m Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n kh\u00f4ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng \u1edf Brazil, v\u00e0 NHM \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf hoa Anh \u0111\u00e0o \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng chu k\u1ef3 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ba Lan kh\u00f3 c\u1ea3n b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ba Lan \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c, h\u1ecd gi\u00e0nh 8/10 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ebfn Nga. V\u1edbi th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c c\u00f9ng phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t cao g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, h\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng H.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ba Lan bi loai sau 2 tran thua lien tiep\" title=\"Ba Lan b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i sau 2 tr\u1eadn thua li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/Nhung-diem-nhan-Ba-Lan-vs-Colombia---Bang-H-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ba Lan b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i sau 2 tr\u1eadn thua li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, &ldquo;\u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng tr\u1eafng&rdquo; \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng n\u01a1i NHM khi ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. Hai l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0o. Ba Lan thua 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Senegal v\u00e0 sau \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i mu\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t 0-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Colombia.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBa Lan ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c Robert Lewandowski, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi t\u1edbi 15 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i. S\u1ed1 9 c\u1ee7a &ldquo;\u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng tr\u1eafng&rdquo; \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trong hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Senegal v\u00e0 Colombia ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Real ch\u01a1i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng, anh d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 7 l\u1ea7n nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n n\u00e0o.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLewandowski b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 theo k\u00e8m qu\u00e1 ch\u1eb7t d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m, ngo\u00e0i ra c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c anh kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 tr\u1ee3 gi\u00fap t\u1eeb c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bi loai khoi World Cup 2018,  Robert Lewandowski che cau thu Ba Lan thiet chat luong.\" title=\"B\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi World Cup 2018,  Robert Lewandowski ch\u00ea c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Ba Lan thi\u1ebft ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/thua-colombia-robert-lewandowski-che-cau-thu-ba-lan-thiet-chat-luong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ba Lan ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o Robert Lewandowski&nbsp;</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i nh\u01b0ng tr\u1eadn Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n vs Ba Lan \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u1eabn s\u1ebd chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00ec danh d\u1ef1.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBa Lan h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh v\u00e0 c\u0169ng s\u1edf h\u1eefu nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n, song h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i thua k\u00e9m \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u. R\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tinh th\u1ea7n v\u00e0 kh\u00e1t khao \u0111i ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n s\u1ebd th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n khi\u1ebfn Ba Lan g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Nhat Ban vs Ba Lan\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n vs Ba Lan\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/Nhat-Ban-vs-Ba-Lan-(4-2-3-1-vs-4-2-3-1).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n vs Ba Lan</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong> D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: 1-1</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"662","checkdouble":"189813"},{"date":"08:34 28/06","title":"Panama vs Tunisia (01h00 ng\u00e0y 29/6): L\u1eddi chia tay ng\u1ecdt ng\u00e0o","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/panama-vs-tunisia-01h00-ngay-296-loi-chia-tay-ngot-ngao.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i, b\u1edfi v\u1eady c\u1ea3 2 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Panama vs Tunisia b\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nPanama v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch l\u1ecbch s\u1eed<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i VCK World Cup 2018 sau giai \u0111o\u1ea1n v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Trung M\u1ef9 \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn ra s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t l\u1edbn \u1edf ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh. Sau 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 qua, h\u1ecd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh bia \u0111\u1ec3 2 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3ng G (Anh v\u00e0 B\u1ec9) t\u1eadp b\u1eafn, v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 9 l\u1ea7n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u1eb7t b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 l\u1ebd, ch\u00ednh c\u00e1c C\u0110V c\u1ee7a qu\u1ed1c gia n\u00e0y c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng mong ch\u1edd Panama l\u00e0m n\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u k\u1ef3 di\u1ec7u. V\u1edbi h\u1ecd, ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ni\u1ec1m vui, v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tham d\u1ef1 World Cup \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 t\u00edch. H\u01a1n n\u1eefa, ch\u1eb3ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n \u0111\u00f3 sao? Pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Baloy gi\u00fap \u0110T n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i World Cup, m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch l\u1ecbch s\u1eed.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1edfi v\u1eady trong <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/video/clip-ban-thang-anh-vs-panama-461-189431.html\" target=\"_blank\">th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t v\u00e1n tennis tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T Anh</span>, ch\u1eb3ng ai trong s\u1ed1 C\u0110V c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd tr\u00ean kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y bu\u1ed3n phi\u1ec1n. Tr\u00e1i l\u1ea1i, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 Panama \u0103n m\u1eebng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0y nh\u01b0 gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 n\u00e9t \u0111\u1eb9p c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1. K\u1ebb y\u1ebfu c\u00f3 c\u00e1ch t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a k\u1ebb y\u1ebfu.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Panama vs Tunisia b\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 1\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Panama vs Tunisia b\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/Nhan-dinh-Panama-vs-Tunisia-bang-G-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110T Panama \u0103n m\u1eebng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed World Cup</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ec9 ra \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u0169ng b\u1eb1ng th\u1eeba. Ngay c\u1ea3 ch\u00ednh b\u00e0n th\u1eafng l\u1ecbch s\u1eed m\u00e0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Baloy ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, c\u0169ng xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb s\u1ef1 h\u00e0o ph\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0110T Anh, khi h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee9ng c\u1ea3 l\u1ea1i \u1edf t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i ra, \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Baloy chinh chi\u1ebfn, anh s\u1ebd gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7 ngay sau World Cup, v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c n\u00e0o t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Panama quy\u1ebft chi\u1ebfn trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. H\u1ecd s\u1ebd l\u00e0m t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn v\u00ec c\u00e1c C\u0110V c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Panama vs Tunisia b\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"C\u0110V Panama c\u00f3 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/panama.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>C\u0110V Panama c\u00f3 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nTunisia h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 2 \u00f4ng k\u1eb9 Anh v\u00e0 B\u1ec9 khi\u1ebfn c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp d\u00e0nh cho \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n ch\u00e2u Phi l\u00e0 b\u1eb1ng kh\u00f4ng. Sau 2 tr\u1eadn, d\u00f9 c\u00f3 kh\u00e1 kh\u1ea9m h\u01a1n Panama \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00fat, nh\u01b0ng \u0110T Tunisia c\u0169ng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u1eb7t b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ebfn 7 l\u1ea7n. \u1ede chi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u00f3 m\u00ecnh 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, v\u00e0 gi\u1edd l\u00e0 l\u00fac \u0111i t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0110T Anh, Tunisia c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. H\u1ecd ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi Tam S\u01b0 b\u1eb1ng qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi l\u00e0m chao \u0111\u1ea3o h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0110T B\u1ec9 b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng pha \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh. 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Courtois cho th\u1ea5y, Tunisia c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111e d\u1ecda nh\u1eefng h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, Tunisia c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n 1 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu h\u01a1n l\u00e0 Panama. M\u1ed9t, \u0111\u00e3 40 n\u0103m k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u00e0 duy nh\u1ea5t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico (1978), \u0111\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng v\u00f9ng Carthage v\u1eabn m\u1ea3i mi\u1ebft \u0111i t\u00ecm con m\u1ed3i ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Hai, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ph\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd ghi \u0111\u1ebfn 4 b\u00e0n t\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup (n\u0103m nay \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 3 b\u00e0n).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Panama vs Tunisia b\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" title=\"Tunisia c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1eb9p t\u1ea1i World Cup\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/tunisia.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Tunisia c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1eb9p t\u1ea1i World Cup</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n\u0110\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd, chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico &ndash; c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb khu v\u1ef1c CONCACAF, t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 Panama v\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam nay. V\u00e0 trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 15 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh t\u1ea1i ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh, Tunisia mu\u1ed1n l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi l\u00ean m\u00e1y bay v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea3 2 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng v\u00ec th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y k\u00e9m ph\u1ea7n h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed n\u1ebfu so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi c\u1ee5c di\u1ec7n &ldquo;tranh nhau ng\u00f4i nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng&rdquo; gi\u1eefa Anh vs B\u1ec9, c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y c\u00f2n \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i h\u01a1n. C\u1ea3 Panama v\u00e0 Tunisia \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t, \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn h\u1ebft kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng, v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Panama vs Tunisia b\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 4\" title=\"Preview Panama vs Tunisia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/Panama-vs-Tunisia.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Panama vs Tunisia b\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h2>Th\u00f4ng tin b\u00ean l\u1ec1<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- C\u1ea3 Tunisia v\u00e0 Panama \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i khi ch\u01b0a gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0o, th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t 7 v\u00e0 9 b\u00e0n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Tunisia m\u1edbi c\u00f3 duy nh\u1ea5t 1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u00e1c k\u1ef3 World Cup.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Panama v\u1eeba ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i World Cup.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>T\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Panama thi\u1ebfu v\u1eafng 2 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t Michael Murillo v\u00e0 Armando Cooper v\u00ec \u00e1n treo gi\u00f2.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn, \u0110T Tunisia c\u0169ng m\u1ea5t 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Mouez Hassen, Syam Ben Youssef v\u00e0 Dylan Bronn v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Panama vs Tunisia b\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 5\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Panama vs Tunisia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/Panama-vs-Tunisia-(4-3-3-vs-4-3-3).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Panama vs Tunisia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h2>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 Panama vs Tunisia: 2-3<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Panama vs Tunisia b\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 6\" title=\"X\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng b\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018 tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/G.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>X\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng b\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018 tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/anh-ha-guc-tunisia-mot-cdv-nhay-len-nap-capo-an-mung-421-188942.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/anh-ha-guc-tunisia-mot-cdv-nhay-len-nap-capo-an-mung.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/anh-ha-guc-tunisia-mot-cdv-nhay-len-nap-capo-an-mung-421-188942.html\">Anh h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Tunisia, m\u1ed9t C\u0110V&hellip; nh\u1ea3y l\u00ean n\u1eafp capo \u0103n m\u1eebng</span><br>\r\nSong song v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c si\u00eau sao t\u1ea1i VCK World Cup 2018, c\u00e1c kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 tr\u00ean kh\u1eafp th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi c\u0169ng lu\u00f4n bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch \u0103n m\u1eebng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, m\u1ed9t C\u0110V...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/dt-panama-roi-world-cup-2018-khi-giac-mo-khep-lai-466-189448.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/24/dt-panama-roi-world-cup-2018-khi-giac-mo-khep-lai.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/dt-panama-roi-world-cup-2018-khi-giac-mo-khep-lai-466-189448.html\">\u0110T Panama s\u1edbm r\u1eddi World Cup 2018: Khi gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i</span><br>\r\n\u0110T Panama r\u1eddi World Cup 2018 ch\u1ec9 sau hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 c\u1ee7a qu\u1ed1c gia Trung M\u1ef9 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i c\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng d\u01b0 v\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t.</div>\r\n</div>\r\nNguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"661","checkdouble":"189814"},{"date":"08:53 28/06","title":"HLV Brazil n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Serbia?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/ngoi-sao-thu-5-va-nhung-giac-mo-con-dang-do.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Tite ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Brazil vs Serbia, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 57 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Selecao c\u00e0ng ch\u01a1i c\u00e0ng hay \u1edf World Cup 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Brazil ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nR\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng nay, Brazil b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Serbia trong l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng b\u1ea3ng E World Cup 2018. V\u1edbi 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c sau hai tr\u1eadn, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Nam M\u1ef9 ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n h\u00f2a l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Brazil v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Tite ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Brazil vs Serbia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Tite ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Brazil vs Serbia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/HLV-Tite-phat-bieu-ve-tran-Brazil-vs-Serbia-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Brazil \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Serbia 2-0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNeymar v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ngay sau ti\u1ebfng c\u00f2i khai cu\u1ed9c, s\u1ee9c \u00e9p m\u00e0 h\u1ecd t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1p b\u1eb1ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 do c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Paulinho. Sang hi\u1ec7p thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 2, Thiago Silva c\u00f2n ghi th\u00eam 1 b\u00e0n n\u1eefa cho Selecao.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Serbia, Brazil \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng E. H\u1ecd s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Mexico, \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 2 b\u1ea3ng F \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nD\u00f9 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Serbia nh\u01b0ng Brazil ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1eaft, theo \u0111\u00f3 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/brazil-nhan-tin-du-sau-khi-danh-bai-serbia-469-189804.html\" target=\"_blank\">Marcelo d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00e1 n\u1eb7ng</span>. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Tite kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Brazil ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Tite ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Brazil vs Serbia, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 57 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Selecao c\u00e0ng ch\u01a1i c\u00e0ng hay \u1edf World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Tite phat bieu ve tran Brazil vs Serbia\" title=\"HLV Tite ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Brazil vs Serbia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/ngoi-sao-thu-5-va-nhung-giac-mo-con-dang-do.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Tite ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Brazil vs Serbia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t d\u1ea7n l\u00ean \u1edf World Cup 2018 v\u1ec1 c\u1ea3 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n v\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n. \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1eb7p Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i n\u00f3ng v\u1ed9i v\u00e0 c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n ch\u1ee7 quan, nh\u01b0ng Brazil \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t l\u00ean\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cBrazil \u0111\u00e3 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t t\u1ed1t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc Serbia, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng d\u1ed3n d\u1eadp nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. T\u00f4i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cNh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111ang ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t d\u1ea7n l\u00ean Brazil c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eebng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"660","checkdouble":"189815"},{"date":"08:47 28/06","title":"Senegal vs Colombia (21h00 ng\u00e0y 28/6): Chi\u1ebfn binh c\u00f2n s\u00f3t l\u1ea1i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/28/senegal-vs-colombia-21h00-ngay-286-chien-binh-con-sot-lai.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft b\u1ea3ng H t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ebd th\u1eb3ng ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng trong. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Senegal vs Colombia t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018.\r\n</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nS\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh s\u01b0 t\u1eed Teranga</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 Tunisia l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u Phi \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ee9 h\u1ea1ng cao nh\u1ea5t FIFA t\u1ea1i VCK World Cup l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, nh\u01b0ng \u0110T Senegal m\u1edbi l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a l\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ecba \u0111en. H\u1ecd v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i v\u1edbi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i, v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady \u1edf k\u1ef3 World Cup hi\u1ec7n gi\u1edd.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ngo\u00e0i k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng, Sadio Mane v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u Phi duy nh\u1ea5t c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp &ndash; sau khi l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t nh\u1eefng Ai C\u1eadp, Ma R\u1ed1c, Nigeria v\u00e0 Tunisia ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf World Cup l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u00e1 t\u1ea7m. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Senegal v\u1eabn \u0111ang c\u1ea1nh tranh quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng H, v\u00e0 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n Ba Lan v\u00e0 Colombia tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m di\u1ec5n ra World Cup, nh\u01b0ng Senegal \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 xem th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/tuong-thuat-ba-lan-vs-senegal-463-188940.html\" target=\"_blank\">S\u01b0 t\u1eed v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng tr\u1eafng b\u1eb1ng l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng</span>, \u0111\u1eadm ch\u1ea5t&hellip; ch\u00e2u \u00c2u tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Senegal vs Colombia b\u1ea3ng H World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Senegal vs Colombia b\u1ea3ng H World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/Nhan-dinh-Senegal-vs-Colombia-bang-H-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110T Senegal g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf \u1edf gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu \u0111ang chinh chi\u1ebfn t\u1ea1i l\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ecba gi\u00e0, Senegal bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd ch\u1eb3ng l\u1ea1 l\u1eabm trong vi\u1ec7c t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng k\u1ef3 t\u00edch. HLV hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Senegal, Aliou Cisse v\u1ed1n l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia t\u1ea1i World Cup 2002, gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft trong l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Senegal l\u00e0 b\u00e0i to\u00e1n kh\u00f3 v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o, khi c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 nguy hi\u1ec3m trong nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng. Tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 HLV Aliou Cisse c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng khen ng\u1ee3i. C\u00f3 ch\u0103ng, h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu \u1edf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7, khi d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng b\u1ecb th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n c\u00f3 tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng, Senegal s\u1ebd \u0111i ti\u1ebfp n\u1ebfu gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Colombia. Nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i, v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng y\u1ebfu \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1eabn c\u00f2n t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i, s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n ch\u00e2u Phi h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m h\u01a1n nh\u01b0 Colombia &ndash; nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mane se doi dau Jame Rodriguez trong tran Senegal vs Colomnbia\" title=\"Mane s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Jame Rodriguez trong tr\u1eadn Senegal vs Colomnbia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/co.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mane s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Jame Rodriguez trong tr\u1eadn Senegal vs Colomnbia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Colombia v\u00e0 gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 dang d\u1edf<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">G\u00e2y ti\u1ebfng vang l\u1edbn \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc (2014) v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, ch\u1ec9 g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Brazil &ndash; \u0110T Colombia n\u0103m \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 tr\u00ecnh l\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 James Rodriguez. Cho \u0111\u1ebfn nay, \u0111\u00f3 v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi l\u00e0 th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 v\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Colombia, v\u1edbi s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh tr\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u1eafp 3 tuy\u1ebfn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau 4 n\u0103m, l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00e0y c\u00f2n \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm h\u01a1n bao gi\u1edd h\u1ebft, khi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam kinh nghi\u1ec7m. Nh\u01b0ng ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd, b\u1edfi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0 \u0111i \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3. Tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi giai \u0111o\u1ea1n 2014 khi Colombia cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 tr\u1ebb trung v\u00e0 l\u00f4i cu\u1ed1n trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1ea7y c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn, l\u00fac n\u00e0y h\u1ecd \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 nh\u01b0 c\u0169.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">James Rodriguez, Juan Cuadrado v\u00e0 Radamel Falcao nh\u01b0 \u00e1nh b\u00ecnh minh 4 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc, nh\u01b0ng gi\u1edd l\u1ea1i \u0111ang tr\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng t\u00ecm l\u1ea1i ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh. Th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 ti\u1ebfp theo l\u1ea1i qu\u00e1 non kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 g\u00e1nh v\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. B\u1edfi v\u1eady, \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Jose Pekerman t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n, v\u00e0 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/tuong-thuat-colombia-vs-nhat-ban-463-188923.html\" target=\"_blank\">Clolombia b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</span> b\u1edfi sai l\u1ea7m c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n \u0111\u00e1ng tr\u00e1ch (Sanchez \u0103n th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf ngay \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cuadrado va cac dong doi an mung sau khi ghi ban thu ba giup Colombia huy diet Ba Lan.\" title=\"Cuadrado v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0103n m\u1eebng sau khi ghi b\u00e0n th\u1ee9 ba gi\u00fap Colombia h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t Ba Lan.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/16.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Li\u1ec7u Colombia c\u00f3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u1edf l\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga?</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u00ednh th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a Colombia gian nan h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. Sau 2 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn, h\u1ecd \u0111ang x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 3, ch\u1ec9 h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i l\u00e0 Ba Lan. \u0110\u00e0nh r\u1eb1ng, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9 \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t, nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng Ba Lan \u0111\u00e3 sa s\u00fat th\u1ea3m h\u1ea1i \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, Colombia c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ed1 ph\u1eadn, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Senegal kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n nh\u01b0 h\u1ecd t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng c\u00f3 khi c\u00f2n l\u00e0m h\u1ea1i Falcao c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, khi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng t\u00ecm ra ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n kh\u1eafc ch\u1ebf.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, Colombia v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nguy\u00ean c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 kh\u00f4ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 mong ch\u1edd Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng gi\u1edd. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng, h\u1ecd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua S\u01b0 t\u1eed Teranga, d\u00f9 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau n\u00e0y c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng h\u1ec1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Preview Senegal vs Colombia\" title=\"Preview Senegal vs Colombia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/Senegal-vs-Colombia.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Senegal vs Colombia b\u1ea3ng H World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Th\u00f4ng tin b\u00ean l\u1ec1<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Senegal l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n ch\u00e2u Phi duy nh\u1ea5t c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Senegal v\u00e0 Colombia \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p nhau 1 l\u1ea7n trong tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu n\u0103m 2014, 2 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00f2a nhau 2-2.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Senegal m\u1edbi ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n 1 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Nam M\u1ef9 t\u1ea1i World Cup, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 3-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Uruguay n\u0103m 2002.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Senegal b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong 11 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i World Cup.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Senegal ghi \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 2 b\u00e0n trong 6 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i World Cup.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Senegal ch\u01b0a thua m\u1ed7i khi Sadio Mane ghi b\u00e0n (th\u1eafng 9, h\u00f2a 6).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Colombia ghi 4 b\u00e0n sau 7 c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch t\u1ea1i World Cup, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 3 b\u00e0n t\u1eeb 4 c\u00fa s\u00fat tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ba Lan.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">-James Rodriguez g\u00f3p d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y v\u00e0o 10 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 7 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n t\u1ea1i World Cup (6 b\u00e0n, 4 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>T\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Senegal c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t, v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u1eef nguy\u00ean s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 gi\u1ed1ng tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Colombia thi\u1ebfu v\u1eafng Abel Aguilar v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Ba Lan. Carlos Sanchez s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i khi m\u00e3n h\u1ea1n treo gi\u00f2 (nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n), nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 v\u1ebb HLV Pekerman \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t ni\u1ec1m tin n\u01a1i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Senegal vs Colombia\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Senegal vs Colombia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/world-cup-giac-mo-cua-the-gioi-va-nhung-giot-nuoc-mat.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Senegal vs Colombia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 Senegal vs Colombia: 2-2<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Xep hang bang G World Cup 2018 truoc luot tran cuoi\" title=\"X\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng b\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018 tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/H.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>X\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng b\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018 tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/dt-senegal-sang-cua-di-tiep-tieng-gam-su-tu-vong-ve-465-189459.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/20/dt-senegal-sang-cua-di-tiep-tieng-gam-su-tu-vong-ve.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/dt-senegal-sang-cua-di-tiep-tieng-gam-su-tu-vong-ve-465-189459.html\">\u0110T Senegal s\u00e1ng c\u1eeda \u0111i ti\u1ebfp: Ti\u1ebfng g\u1ea7m s\u01b0 t\u1eed v\u1ecdng v\u1ec1</span><br>\r\n\u0110T Senegal x\u1ee9ng v\u1edbi bi\u1ec7t danh c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd khi m\u1ed7i l\u1ea7n xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n l\u1ea1i g\u1ea7m vang m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, nh\u01b0 c\u00e1ch s\u01b0 t\u1eed r\u00ecnh r\u1eadp r\u1ed3i b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd lao ra b\u1eaft g\u1ecdn con m\u1ed3i tr\u00ean th\u1ea3o nguy\u00ean...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/khong-dep-trai-ngoi-ngoi-thuyen-truong-senegal-van-an-tuong-nhat-world-cup-421-189068.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/20/khong-dep-trai-ngoi-ngoi-thuyen-truong-senegal-van-an-tuong-nhat-world-cup.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/khong-dep-trai-ngoi-ngoi-thuyen-truong-senegal-van-an-tuong-nhat-world-cup-421-189068.html\">Kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb9p trai ng\u1eddi ng\u1eddi, thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Senegal v\u1eabn \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t World Cup</span><br>\r\nNg\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i qua l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, v\u00e0 HLV Aliou Cisse g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 World Cup v\u1edbi phong c\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/cuc-dien-bang-h-tr